# Test selection — tagged suites, affected runs, merge tiers

Suites grow over time. **Do not run full product regression on every commit.** Run what the diff can break; run everything before **master**.

## Tags (Playwright wb-regression)

Canonical registry: [`tests/test-tags.ts`](../../tests/test-tags.ts).

| Tag | Domain |
|-----|--------|
| `@wb-sync` | Umbrella — all relay tutor+student specs |
| `@wb-strokes` | Draw / move / page isolation |
| `@wb-viewport` | Pan/zoom, follow oracle |
| `@wb-assets` | Image + PDF on canvas |
| `@wb-presence` | Join, welcome, exit/rejoin |
| `@wb-graph` | GraphEmbeddable + graphStateJson |
| `@wb-recording` | Recording FSM / banner copy |
| `@wb-chrome` | Toolbars, rails, flyouts, layout |
| `@wb-av` | Live A/V mesh / reconnect |

**New tests:** add domain tag(s) on the `test()` or `test.describe()` — see [`playwright-on-fix.mdc`](playwright-on-fix.mdc).

**Adjacency:** `wb-test-select` expands tags cautiously (e.g. `@wb-graph` → also `@wb-sync` + `@wb-strokes`). When in doubt, add a tag.

## Commands

| Command | When |
|---------|------|
| `npm run test:wb-affected` | Dry-run: diff → tags + commands |
| `npm run test:wb-affected:run -- --base origin/<parent>` | Execute affected jest + Playwright |
| `npm run test:wb-playwright:tags -- @wb-graph` | Explicit tag filter |
| `npm run test:wb-sync` | **Full** wb jest + full wb-regression Playwright (~40 min) |

Path → tag mapping lives in [`scripts/wb-test-select.cjs`](../../scripts/wb-test-select.cjs).

## Merge tiers (orchestrator enforces)

| Merge | Playwright / Jest gate |
|-------|-------------------------|
| **Commit on feature branch** | New fix's tagged test(s) must pass. Optionally `test:wb-affected:run` if touch is broader. |
| **Small branch → parent feature / v1-redesign** | `npm run test:wb-affected:run -- --base origin/<parent>` (+ `npx next build` if build surface). **Err on caution** — if diff is ambiguous or touches `WhiteboardWorkspaceClient`, run extra tags or full `test:wb-sync`. |
| **Large wave / long-running branch (e.g. v1-redesign) integration** | `test:wb-sync` on **final integrated tip** before merge into that branch (existing AGENTS cadence). |
| **Any branch → `master`** | **FULL:** `npm run test:wb-sync` + `npm run test:regression` + `npx next build`. No selective gate. |

**Never** merge to `master` with only affected tags.

## Executor / orchestrator checklist

- [ ] Diff scanned — list tags that will run (or full suite if merge tier requires it).
- [ ] Each new Playwright test has domain tag(s).
- [ ] Handoff states **tags run** vs **full suite** and merge target branch.
- [ ] Andrew's smokebook = **new** UX + hardware judgment only — not re-proofing tagged regressions ([`smoke-when-done.mdc`](smoke-when-done.mdc)).
